WEBVTT

00:03.336 --> 00:05.166
HARRY:
But the service isn't that fast.

00:06.540 --> 00:10.310
Believe me. you guys are gonna flip
over the sushi in this place.

00:10.477 --> 00:12.337
Hey. come in. everybody.

00:12.946 --> 00:15.966
Excuse me. wasn't this
a Japanese restaurant yesterday?

00:16.148 --> 00:19.678
Say. you got the sharp eye for detail.
don't you?

00:19.852 --> 00:20.982
So I've been told.

00:21.153 --> 00:25.323
My name is Panayoti Shakelaris.
but everybody call me Papa Jack.

00:25.624 --> 00:27.824
-Why?
-Why?

00:27.993 --> 00:29.653
[LAUGHS]

00:30.161 --> 00:31.651
I don't know why.

00:32.162 --> 00:33.433
Follow me. please.

00:33.598 --> 00:35.028
What an amusing anecdote.

00:35.200 --> 00:37.000
PAPA JACK:
That's a nice table for you.

00:37.168 --> 00:38.998
Sit. Eat.

00:39.170 --> 00:41.830
Sing. Dance. Enjoy.

00:42.006 --> 00:44.336
You're gonna make us have fun.
aren't you?

00:44.509 --> 00:48.069
-Boy. neat menus.
-It's all Greek to me.

00:48.246 --> 00:49.706
[LAUGHS]

00:51.114 --> 00:54.144
-Is he dangerous?
-No. we'll be fine. thanks.

00:54.317 --> 00:57.717
Guys. wait.
I'll bring special treat for you.

00:58.053 --> 00:59.923
Excuse me.

01:03.592 --> 01:05.692
Did you put a piece of lettuce
in your pocket?

01:05.861 --> 01:08.351
It's for Harvey. My new pet.

01:09.297 --> 01:12.957
Lettuce? Harvey? I get it.
Big. tough Bull's got little pet bunny.

01:13.401 --> 01:14.931
Actually. Harvey's a python.

01:16.136 --> 01:17.126
Oh.

01:17.304 --> 01:18.864
I feed him bunnies. though.

01:19.874 --> 01:22.074
-Could I watch sometime?
-Oh. fellas. please.

01:22.243 --> 01:25.583
Harry. you'd love to see a snake
eat a bunny as much as I would.

01:26.013 --> 01:30.383
-I hope that everybody's hungry.
-Oh. boy. my favorite. Fire.

01:30.551 --> 01:33.681
Hey. this must be the souvlaki.

01:33.854 --> 01:36.654
No. souvlaki doesn't throb.

01:36.824 --> 01:38.994
That's very interesting. What is it?

01:39.158 --> 01:41.678
This is the brand-new specialty
of the house.

01:42.095 --> 01:44.755
Squid swimming in an olive oil base...

01:44.931 --> 01:47.661
...dripping with kasseri and feta cheese...

01:47.834 --> 01:50.864
...bubb|ing over noodles and pine nuts...

01:51.036 --> 01:54.696
...covered in a simmering
lemon garlic sauce.

01:55.674 --> 01:57.774
I'll take scrambled eggs.

01:58.876 --> 02:01.866
Come on. everybody. eat up.

02:04.048 --> 02:08.678
Come on. guys. No reason not to try
something just because it's new. right?

02:09.787 --> 02:11.917
Oh. I can't believe what chickens
you guys are.

02:12.089 --> 02:16.029
Come on. food is not just something to eat.
it's something to celebrate.

02:17.361 --> 02:18.891
Have a ball.

02:26.870 --> 02:29.600
So. what's the verdict?

02:32.208 --> 02:35.198
IGROANINGI

02:43.653 --> 02:45.683
Manslaughter.

